<A>__{a smile creeps onto her terrible face. and she starts towards the little door, moving in an odd, laboring way, as if she had four legs instead of two. she signals the armoire bug to stand aside, her back to coraline. coraline hears the soft chirp of her mother's finger on wet glass! looks around, desperate where is it coming from?! the cat's ears twitch and focus, and then he sees something on the mantel!. he whispers to coraline }
